test_name: DSCOGST compared to Form D1a NORMCOG
short_desc: If NORMCOG = 1, then DSCOGST should equal 1
full_desc: If Form D1a, Q2. NORMCOG (participant have unimpaired cognition & behavior) = 1 (yes), then Q6. DSCOGST (What is the participant’s cognitive status?) should equal 1 (cognitively stable)

test_name: DSCOGST compared to Form D1a MCI
short_desc: If MCI = 1, then DSCOGST should equal 2
full_desc: If Form D1a, Q4b. MCI (participant meets criteria for MCI) = 1 (yes), then Q6. DSCOGST (What is the participant’s cognitive status?) should equal 2 (MCI - DS)

test_name: DSCOGST compared to Form D1a DEMENTED
short_desc: If DEMENTED = 1, then DSCOGST should equal 3
full_desc: If Form D1a, Q3. DEMENTED (participant meet criteria for dementia) = 1 (yes), then Q6. DSCOGST (What is the participant’s cognitive status?) should equal 3 (Dementia)
